```

**Key UI Components Used (from @semparar/design-system-app):**
- `BasicScreen` - Template with Header, ScrollView, error modal
- `DetailTransactionValue` - Hero card showing icon, title, points value
- `TagLabel` - Badge showing transaction date/time
- `SeparatorHorizontal` - Divider line
- `CardActivity` - Clickable activity card (used in contact modal)
- `BackDropBottom` - Bottom sheet modal for "Report Problem"
- `Box`, `Text`, `Button` - Layout and typography

